6	//! Function body translation: MIR → `mir.func`.
7	//!
8	//! Translates complete MIR function bodies into `dialect-mir` `mir.func` operations.
9	//!
10	//! # Responsibilities
11	//!
12	//! - Extract function signature (arguments, return type)
13	//! - Create and link pliron IR basic blocks (entry block carries function
14	//!   parameters; every other block is argument-less)
15	//! - Emit one `mir.alloca` per non-ZST MIR local at the top of the entry
16	//!   block and record the slot in [`ValueMap`]
17	//! - Translate every reachable block in order; unwind-only cleanup blocks
18	//!   are patched with `mir.unreachable`
19	//! - Detect compile-time kernel attributes (`#[cluster(...)]`,
20	//!   `#[launch_bounds(...)]`)
